don't know anybody. I'll go next year.

46:11.240 --> 46:12.840
Wait, what is this? OK, what?

46:12.920 --> 46:15.120
-I'm not feeling it.
-You kidding me or what?

46:15.200 --> 46:17.960
Think they'll keep a spot for you
all nice and cozy there?

46:18.040 --> 46:19.320
I decided not to go.

46:19.960 --> 46:23.520
What the fuck are you doing?Oh!

46:26.120 --> 46:26.960
Alright.

